---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/base.astro";
import PageIntro from "../components/page-intro.astro";
import HeadshotCard from "../components/headshot-card.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="about · colin vargas"
  description="about colin vargas, aerospace engineering graduate student and computational systems builder."
  active="about"
>
  <PageIntro
    eyebrow="about / identity layer"
    title="engineering tastefully suspicious systems."
    description="i work somewhere between aerospace engineering, numerical methods, propulsion, and the part of computing where a server starts screaming at 3:17 a.m. for reasons known only to god and systemd."
  />

  <section class="about-grid">
    <div class="about-copy surface-panel">
      <p>
        i’m colin vargas, an aerospace engineering master’s student at asu with a
        focus on computational fluid dynamics, numerical methods, and propulsion.
        my long-term interest is building simulation tools that can handle messy,
        non-ideal physics without pretending the universe is a clean textbook problem.
      </p>

      <p>
        right now, that means growing from foundational finite-volume and advection
        solvers toward higher-order, amr-capable navier-stokes work, with an eye
        toward combustion, evaporation, multiphase behavior, and gas-turbine-relevant
        flows.
      </p>

      <p>
        outside the formal research lane, i’m building out personal infrastructure
        under <strong>urmom.systems</strong>: status pages, dashboards, monitoring,
        automation, and public-facing systems that look polished while quietly doing
        useful work. civilization was apparently not going to organize itself.
      </p>
    </div>

    <HeadshotCard />
  </section>

  <section id="contact" class="surface-panel contact-band">
  <div>
    <p class="eyebrow">contact</p>
    <h2>send the packet.</h2>
    <p>
      for research, engineering, teaching, infrastructure, or professional opportunities,
      email is the cleanest route.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="contact-actions">
    <a class="button primary" href="mailto:your-email@example.com">
      email me
    </a>

    <a class="button ghost" href="https://github.com/urmom6009">
      github
    </a>

    <a class="button ghost" href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/your-linkedin">
      linkedin
    </a>
  </div>
  </section>

  <section class="continuity-strip">
    <div>
      <span class="eyebrow">focus</span>
      <strong>cfd · propulsion · numerical methods</strong>
    </div>

    <div>
      <span class="eyebrow">stack</span>
      <strong>c++ · python · astro · linux · cloudflare</strong>
    </div>

    <div>
      <span class="eyebrow">status</span>
      <strong>building, unfortunately</strong>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

